&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop secure, scalable, and maintainable APIs&lt;/strong&gt; (primarily Python; Java experience also valued).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate closely&lt;/strong&gt; with the existing two-person AI pod to explore, prototype, and productize AI solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate with &lt;strong&gt;LLM APIs&lt;/strong&gt; (OpenAI, Gemini) and &lt;strong&gt;vector databases&lt;/strong&gt; to enhance automation initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner cross-functionally&lt;/strong&gt; with Product, Customer Success, and Sales teams to identify opportunities for AI assistance and build AI expertise across the company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advocate for and apply healthy coding practices&lt;/strong&gt; and Agile methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate actively in &lt;strong&gt;code reviews, pair programming, and knowledge development&lt;/strong&gt; to implement new code and debug existing systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide &lt;strong&gt;2nd tier production support &lt;/strong&gt;and proactively identify ways to improve our systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build financial and cleantech subject matter expertise&lt;/strong&gt; and stay abreast of new AI technologies and industry trends to inform engineering decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strong programming experience &lt;/strong&gt;in Python or Java; comfort in learning the other.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Demonstrated experience&lt;/strong&gt; with LLMs, AI APIs, or applied ML workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solid understanding &lt;/strong&gt;of REST APIs, testing frameworks, and cloud deployment (AWS preferred).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Provide thought leadership &lt;/strong&gt;that challenges existing processes and delivers clear, structured decision-making frameworks to evaluate implementation tradeoffs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Curiosity&lt;/strong&gt;, pragmatism, and ability to move from prototype to production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clear communicator &lt;/strong&gt;who enjoys solving problems collaboratively&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Genuine &lt;strong&gt;enthusiasm for Banyan&#39;s mission&lt;/strong&gt; and a willingness to help and mentor other team members.&lt;/li&gt;
